examples.en: The lyrics have been subtly altered.
Certainly the relationship has changed subtly.
Her appearance had changed, subtly but perceptibly.
examples.ru: Ее внешность изменилась, неуловимо, но ощутимо.

examples.en: This emphasis is subtly reinforced by the format of each book.
examples.ru: Этот акцент слегка усиливается форматом каждой книги.
